013package org.apache.juneau.rest.logger;
014
015import org.apache.juneau.cp.*;
016
017/**
018 * Default implementation of a {@link CallLogger} that never logs REST calls.
019 *
020 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
021 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="../../../../../index.html#jrs.LoggingAndDebugging">Logging / Debugging</a>
022 * </ul>
023 */
024public class BasicDisabledCallLogger extends CallLogger {
025
026   /**
027    * Constructor.
028    *
029    * @param beanStore The bean store containing injectable beans for this logger.
030    */
031   public BasicDisabledCallLogger(BeanStore beanStore) {
032      super(beanStore);
033   }
034
035   @Override
036   protected Builder init(BeanStore beanStore) {
037      return super.init(beanStore).disabled();
038   }
039}
